title: Photos: Sean Lee, Terrance Williams among Cowboys pitching in to help Dallas school's athletic field
text: Terrance Williams of the Dallas Cowboys unloads grass turf to be placed on the athletic field of St. Philip's School & Community Center in Dallas, Texas Saturday Oct. 17, 2015. The Cowboys and Sports Illustrated worked together to assist the school. (Ron T. Ennis/Special Contributor)
